rows.label: qst104709_msg001
rows.name: 座礁した船はまかせろ(仮)

rows.label: qst104709_msg002
rows.name:
あなた方にお願いしたいことがあるので
グーラで合流しましょう(仮)

rows.label: qst104709_msg0001
rows.name:
My husband and the others went with
a Blade to look for help. They went
into the cloudway over there.

rows.label: qst104709_msg0002
rows.name:
She doesn't have her Driver with
her so I suggested she stay behind,
but she didn't listen.

rows.label: qst104709_msg0101
rows.name:
My husband's safe! Thank the stars.
Phew, I was worried there for a bit.

rows.label: qst104709_msg0102
rows.name:
I should prepare so we're ready for
when they come back.
